sentences.sentence: Ranges also support more complex initializations.
sentences.translation: 范围还支持更复杂的初始化。

sentences.sentence: The first thing is what we're going to call "initializations."
sentences.translation: 第一个事情是我们叫做的“初始化。”

sentences.sentence: You can use one line or two in your own variable initializations.
sentences.translation: 可以在自己的变量初始化中使用一行或两行。
